https://www.english-room.com/grammar/pronouns_object_01_dd.htm
1. The boy is singing. Look at him.
2. The girl is swimming. Look at her.
3. The dog is running. Look at it.
4. I am reading. Look at me.
5. You are painting. Look at you.
6. My mother is kind. I like her.
7. Where are you? I cannot see you.
8. I like your cat. How old is it?
9. I am hungry. The sandwich is for me.
10. My father is thirsty. The water is for him.
